  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42500</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_179_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ええと……これが&lt;Chester&gt;さん用で、
これが&lt;Cless&gt;さん用……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Uhm... this is &lt;Chester&gt;'s portion, and
this is &lt;Cless&gt;'s portion...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_179_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああっ！
&lt;Mint&gt;、またやってるの、そんなこと！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mint&gt;! Are you doing that again?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_179_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何なんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What? Is there something wrong?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_179_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さんはポークが好きなので、
ポークの入っているの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm merely putting pork in &lt;Cless&gt;' plate 
because he likes pork.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42900</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_179_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Chester&gt;さんはチキンが好きなので、
チキンの入っている料理を作ってるんです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>While I'm chooking chicken for &lt;Chester&gt;
because he likes it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43004</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_179_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか……&lt;Mint&gt;さんって
気配り上手なんですね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ohh...! You're a really thoughtful
person, &lt;Mint&gt;....</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43080</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_179_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大所帯のお料理は大変です</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's truly tiring to cook for a
large household.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_179_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし！　わたしも&lt;Mint&gt;さんを見習います！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Alright! I'll also follow &lt;Mint&gt;'s example.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43280</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_179_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;ちゃんまで！　ダメだって！
男どもを甘やかしちゃ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even you, &lt;Mel&gt;!? You can't!
Those boys are going to get spoiled!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
